---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Deczer Solution">
	<main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
		<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-10 text-white">Privacy Policy</h1>
		
		<div class="prose prose-invert text-slate-400 space-y-6">
			<section>
				<h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">1. General Information</h2>
				<p>The protection of your personal data is important to me. This policy explains how I handle data when you visit my website.</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">2. Server Log Files</h2>
				<p>Since this website is self-hosted on my own infrastructure, the web server (Nginx) automatically collects and stores information in "server log files", which your browser automatically transmits to me. These are:</p>
				<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
					<li>IP address (anonymized if configured)</li>
					<li>Date and time of the server request</li>
					<li>Browser type and version</li>
					<li>Operating system used</li>
					<li>Referrer URL</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="mt-2">This data is purely technical and used to ensure the stability and security of the server. The legal basis for this is Art. 6 (1) (f) GDPR.</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">3. Cookies</h2>
				<p>This website is designed to be privacy-friendly. It currently <strong>does not use any cookies</strong> or tracking scripts (like Google Analytics).</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">4. Your Rights</h2>
				<p>You have the right to request information about your stored personal data at any time. You also have the right to request the correction, blocking, or deletion of this data.</p>
			</section>

			<section class="p-6 bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl">
				<h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Contact for Data Privacy</h2>
				<p>If you have any questions, please contact me at:</p>
				<p class="text-cyan-400 mt-2">[Your Email Address]</p>
			</section>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>